<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/108105-for-those-who-have-finished-the-book-my">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[For those who have FINISHED the book: My question is: What DID happen to Rabina's last child that she was brought to Polly Shine for (or was there even a child?) <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
